{"id": "1451538467493380229", "channel_id": "1451538467493380229", "type": 0, "author_id": "733642654293950484", "author_name": "kk0689", "author_bot": false, "content": "一則無心的諭言\n一艘偏離航線的船\n編織著命運的線\n一切隨著夢沉入海中\n…\n\n「不要再吞咽這裡的水了。」\n「停止呼吸，余會帶你回到現實。」\n「……余剛剛說了，停止呼吸。」\n\nUID:100105605\n\n（因為是即興創作所以畫面會比較零散一點，還有這是我第一次在網路上面發同人作品，謝謝大家願意看到這裡～)", "timestamp": "2025-12-19T11:35:38.931000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1451538467942305812", "filename": "IMG_0867.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 348325, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451538467493380229/1451538467942305812/IMG_0867.jpg?ex=69cbb18b&is=69ca600b&hm=02b245108828d0c076afc55d0b90d05b9e10e0d06db49dc3e5e33bcb514f675e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451538467493380229", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "圖魯睡覺", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1441261039227240468"]}
